## Important Conventions

- **`AnalysisResults/{alias}/`** always has latest results at root, history in `_History/` subfolders
- **`analyses.json`** is the central index — lists all aliases, run timestamps, program counts
- **SystemAnalyzer.Batch** is the pure C# analysis pipeline (V1 PowerShell scripts archived in `_old/`)
- **AnalysisCommon is a shared repo folder** — not per-alias, not deployed, lives only in the source tree
- **Cache-buster versions** on `graph.js` in `graph.html` — increment `?v=N` after JS changes
- **All libraries are self-hosted** in `wwwroot/lib/` — no CDN dependencies (Edge Tracking Prevention caused issues)
